    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 platform is centered around the high-revving S65 4.0L V8, utilizing eight individual throttle bodies to achieve a linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline. The 6-speed manual transmission offers precise shift throws, sending power through the M Variable Differential Lock for optimal traction out of corners. The suspension remains composed with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) providing adjustable damping rates to suit both spirited canyon runs and daily transit. Significant mechanical upkeep has been prioritized, including recent rod bearing service and throttle actuator replacements to ensure the integrity of the valvetrain and induction system. While the exterior and interior show character consistent with its mileage, the chassis rigidity and engine harmonics remain exceptional.",
